{
  "stem": "4513.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You've got to be able to stand taller than these kinds of things and to walk away and to keep pushing to get rid of the issues that those people are espousing.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've been the-- now that's when I been-- I've spoken before groups.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because several-- Jewish Community Council and all these people have gotten me to speak before various groups.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I've spoken before a group of people who said they didn't believe it, it was all--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, look, let me tell you something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This ain't your mind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't have a picture except in my own mind, but I was there and I saw it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said, are you sure?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were just dreaming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, no, I was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I'm going to tell you something, and I'm gonna tell all of you something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you don't understand this and you don't listen to what people are saying, we are doomed to repeat it again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it makes no sense.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a group out at-- out at the Charlestown Army Veteran's Home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, most of you guys in this room know exactly what the war was like.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You weren't there at Dachau, or at any of the camps, so you're telling me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I'm gonna tell you something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why did we fight the war in the first place?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And who were we fighting?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what was that about?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And think about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a very short step between what you saw in the field and what happened at Dachau.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I told them once again, we know you saw the little kids blown up in England.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You saw all of that.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
